  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 3 \u0b86\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb2\u0bc0\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9f\u0bc0\u0b9a\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Recovery of 3 thousand liters of diesel stored in Vavuniya",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Nelukulam police said that 3000 liters of diesel stored in a popular hardware store in the Veppangulam area in Vavuniya was recovered this afternoon (27) during a special test operation.",
        "Following information received by the Vavuniya Special Police Unit, the Nelukulam Police conducted a search of a popular hotware located in the Veppangulam area on Mannar Road, Vavuniya. 3000 liters of diesel stored in 15 barrels was found in the warehouse area of \u200b\u200bthe hotware.",
        "Police also recovered 3,000 liters of diesel from 15 barrels and arrested a 33-year-old man on duty at the hardware depot on suspicion of possessing it.",
        "Nelukulam police said they have taken further steps to take him to court after further investigations."
      ],
